## Event Handling

| React JSX | Svelte |
|-----------|--------|
| `onClick={fn}` | `onclick={fn}` |
| `onClick={() => fn(id)}` | `onclick={() => fn(id)}` |
| `onClick={e => e.stopPropagation()}` | `onclick:stopPropagation={fn}` or `onclick={(e) => { e.stopPropagation(); fn(); }}` |
| `onChange={e => setVal(e.target.value)}` | `bind:value={val}` |
| `onSubmit={handleSubmit}` | `onsubmit:prevent={handleSubmit}` |
| `onKeyDown={fn}` | `onkeydown={fn}` |

### Controlled Inputs → bind:value

**React:**

```jsx
<input value={name} onChange={e => setName(e.target.value)} />
```

**Svelte:**

```svelte
<input bind:value={name} />
<!-- bind:value is two-way: reads and writes $state variable directly -->
```

