## Layouts

### Persistent Layout in Svelte

```svelte
<!-- resources/js/Layouts/AppLayout.svelte -->
<script>
    let { children } = $props();
</script>

<nav><!-- Navbar --></nav>
<main>
    <!-- {@render children()} renders the page content -->
    {@render children()}
</main>
```

```svelte
<!-- resources/js/Pages/Home.svelte -->
<script>
    import AppLayout from '@/Layouts/AppLayout.svelte';
    import { defineOptions } from '@inertiajs/svelte';

    // Persistent layout — Navbar won't remount on navigation
    defineOptions({ layout: AppLayout });
</script>

<div>Home content</div>
```

