## Common Patterns

### Conditional Rendering

**React:**

```jsx
{isLoading ? <Spinner /> : <Content />}
{items.length > 0 && <List />}
```

**Svelte:**

```svelte
{#if isLoading}
    <Spinner />
{:else}
    <Content />
{/if}

{#if items.length > 0}
    <List {items} />
{/if}
```

### Loops

**React:**

```jsx
{products.map(p => <ProductCard key={p.id} product={p} />)}
```

**Svelte:**

```svelte
{#each products as product (product.id)}
    <ProductCard {product} />
{/each}
<!-- (product.id) is the keyed identifier — equivalent to React's key prop -->
```

### Props Shorthand

```svelte
<!-- When prop name matches variable name, use shorthand -->
<ProductCard {product} />
<!-- Same as: <ProductCard product={product} /> -->
```

### Snippets (replaces React children/slots)

**Svelte 5 — `{@render}`:**

```svelte
<!-- Card.svelte -->
<script>
    let { children, title } = $props();
</script>

<div class="card">
    <h2>{title}</h2>
    {@render children()}
</div>
```

```svelte
<!-- Usage -->
<Card title="Hello">
    <p>Body content</p>
</Card>
```

